Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.04,0:01:53.64,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Once a businessman in Tokyo,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.00,0:01:57.31,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,now I work for a delivery company in the South China Sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.02,0:02:07.60,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,With that, we're done transferring the crates.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.60,0:02:10.15,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Would you please sign this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.40,0:02:18.29,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, could somebody sign this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.95,0:02:25.79,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It usually doesn't work out that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.79,0:02:27.55,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,A pitiful delivery company.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.41,0:02:33.04,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,To eat, we brush up against the law from time to time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.42,0:02:39.22,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So everything's OK, Rock?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.22,0:02:42.39,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,All OK, and I even got them to sign.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.39,0:02:45.56,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We should have a package from them as well. Did you get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.97,0:02:48.23,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well, about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.02,0:02:51.10,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I did get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.10,0:02:52.73,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Is there a problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.73,0:02:57.53,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If not, ask them to use the crane once more and get down here with the package.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.53,0:02:58.24,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.24,0:03:01.25,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So the troublemaker is making something out of himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.78,0:03:06.08,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'd like to say that, but nothing's changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.08,0:03:10.41,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's just that his white collar look was perfect for this job.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.41,0:03:12.12,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So far.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.12,0:03:15.55,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Is he worried about the package?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.09,0:03:17.55,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Seems like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.42,0:03:20.42,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Helpless.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.42,0:03:25.01,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's just a cartel's little errand.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.31,0:03:32.44,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I counted the crates we delivered, like you wanted me to.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.85,0:03:37.15,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And I brought the package here too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.15,0:03:39.91,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Is... he it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.65,0:03:46.31,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Once we've landed, we're handing him over to a certain Colombian mafiosa buyer at a designated point.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.31,0:03:48.85,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Revy, put him in a cabin for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.37,0:03:52.96,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Now, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.29,0:03:56.50,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you fight back.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.50,0:03:57.50,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.67,0:04:01.22,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Come on. Get in this hole.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.18,0:04:09.81,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,He looked like he was gonna puke.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.81,0:04:12.27,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,He's still not a pro.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.02,0:04:17.02,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.86,0:04:20.82,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We're a delivery company.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.78,0:04:24.86,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We take packages to their designated destinations.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.86,0:04:27.62,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's where our resposibilities end.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.62,0:04:28.49,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.49,0:04:30.20,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.20,0:04:32.84,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I won't get too attached to the boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.83,0:04:35.92,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Good boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.01,0:04:48.72,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.72,0:04:49.22,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.22,0:04:52.52,Copy of Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Want me to show you what you had for breakfast?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.83,0:04:55.19,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but would you trade the baby-sitting duty with Revy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.02,0:04:56.49,Copy of Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Get over here! You!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.19,0:04:58.19,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Her professionalism is a problem in itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.19,0:05:00.52,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's no good if the package has holes in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.35,0:04:59.53,Copy of Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Son of a bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.86,0:05:03.74,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Taking advantage of my kindness!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.86,0:05:03.74,Copy of Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Revy...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.74,0:05:05.74,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What are you glaring at?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.74,0:05:05.74,Copy of Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.24,0:05:09.03,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't need something as good as a cabin.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.03,0:05:11.87,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We ought to chain him up and throw him in the hold.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.87,0:05:12.91,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That brat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.91,0:05:15.91,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We're in the middle of the sea. He can't escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.91,0:05:17.37,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We don't need chains.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.37,0:05:18.47,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.46,0:05:23.59,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.59,0:05:25.22,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,it'll only be for a short while,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.22,0:05:28.18,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,but we're going to be on the road together.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.18,0:05:31.47,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you stop throwing food?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.06,0:05:33.56,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I won't say a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.56,0:05:37.45,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Santa Maria sees through all this, you villain.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.60,0:05:44.11,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well, there's not much I can say to that since I'm helping with this kidnapping.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.57,0:05:49.75,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're... different from the tattooed woman or the black man.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.12,0:05:52.91,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You seem like a normal person.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.91,0:05:54.12,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It must seem like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.12,0:05:56.21,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just a villain in training.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.29,0:06:04.13,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The people who put me on the boat didn't tell me anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.13,0:06:06.05,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Am I being sold somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.98,0:06:11.55,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Are you worried?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.43,0:06:15.77,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.77,0:06:17.69,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,My father will save me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.94,0:06:21.11,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Father? Aren't you an orphan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.11,0:06:25.19,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Who said that? The cartel? They're liars.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.57,0:06:29.78,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,My father is a member of one of the great thirteen families of South America.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.78,0:06:32.41,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The 11th head of the Loveless household.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.41,0:06:34.79,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Diego Jose San Fernando Loveless.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.79,0:06:37.25,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm his only son.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.25,0:06:39.12,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'll eventually become the head of the family.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.12,0:06:40.33,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Garcia Loveless.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.33,0:06:42.51,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If you're after pity, stop waisting your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.84,0:06:46.46,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If you're going to lie, you should come up with a better one.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.46,0:06:48.97,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Pity? Don't be stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.97,0:06:51.22,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What could I gain from lying now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.22,0:06:53.64,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're a pretty unlikable kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.64,0:07:00.31,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you hear the name Loveless anyway? It's the lowest noble house of the thirteen families.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.31,0:07:02.40,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Though that makes it a little more believable.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.40,0:07:05.61,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well, things haven't been going well lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.61,0:07:07.86,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But we've been getting by.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.49,0:07:12.57,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Father is a man of good character.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.57,0:07:14.41,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,He never did anything on the side.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.54,0:07:21.42,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Business wasn't going well, but the plantations were stable...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.75,0:07:23.46,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,until the mafia came.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.46,0:07:26.71,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So you were kidnapped by the mafia.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.71,0:07:30.42,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're pretty good at making up stories.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.47,0:07:34.93,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,They came to forcefully buy our land.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.93,0:07:37.60,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,A geological test showed that lanthanides could be found there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.72,0:07:41.85,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,When my father refused, they showed their true selves.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.85,0:07:44.36,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,They began harassing our farms.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.36,0:07:47.32,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But father still wouldn't nod his head.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.32,0:07:49.53,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.53,0:07:50.99,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Lanthanides?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.99,0:07:52.45,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's also called rare earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.86,0:07:55.03,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you know your periodic table?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.03,0:07:55.89,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Good grief.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.45,0:07:58.33,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you learn a word like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.41,0:08:01.79,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You still don't believe me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.79,0:08:02.92,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's fine then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.38,0:08:07.04,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's not that easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.04,0:08:09.25,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What can I do to make you believe me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.25,0:08:12.51,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What else do you know about rare earth?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.05,0:08:18.26,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Lutetium, atomic number 71, was found on our land.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.26,0:08:21.89,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's used as a repairing medium for ceramics.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.89,0:08:22.89,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,How's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.60,0:08:26.86,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No good, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.94,0:08:30.07,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Then the next question:
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.65,0:08:33.40,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The Loveless household has a dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.40,0:08:36.50,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Regarding that dog, what do you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.91,0:08:38.74,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.74,0:08:41.91,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That dog became a member of our family six years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.91,0:08:47.13,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,His name is Lazlo, a white-furred Volpino Italiano.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.96,0:08:51.96,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Revy, Rock is taking too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.63,0:08:58.30,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,He's probably getting himself worked up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.30,0:09:02.94,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,He'll probably give us a sob story and ask us to let him go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.02,0:09:06.35,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Told you. With eyes just like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.77,0:09:12.28,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's odd.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.28,0:09:14.74,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like how this feels.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.59,0:09:19.83,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I think we might want to wait until after we dock to give him to the mafia.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.83,0:09:21.37,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The cartel was lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.99,0:09:24.79,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If they're lying, it means there's trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.79,0:09:25.63,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.12,0:09:30.50,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't have pity for our packages.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.50,0:09:35.05,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to feel like shit, if you imagine where he might end up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.84,0:09:41.60,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But as long as it's profit for our company, there's no problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.60,0:09:45.15,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Understand? There's no problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.98,0:09:49.31,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The world will keep on spinning even if justice doesn't exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.61,0:09:52.65,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'd be lying if I said I didn't pity him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.49,0:09:57.49,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm also concerned that our client lied.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.49,0:10:00.32,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I used to be in the resource investigation department of my company.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.32,0:10:03.16,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I know a lot about rare earth and rare metals.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.16,0:10:05.75,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And he's correct in what he says about the Loveless family.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.66,0:10:09.96,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I remember papers we had from our South American division.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.96,0:10:11.93,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Family structure and whatnot.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.84,0:10:15.88,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Impressive. That's impressive, Rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.88,0:10:18.59,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're a very brilliant businessman.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.59,0:10:23.28,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have to get you some of Mama's homemade cherry pie as a reward.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.81,0:10:28.60,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Either way, it's up to Dutch. I'll go with what he says.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.06,0:10:30.69,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I just don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.69,0:10:35.36,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The moment they had the kid, they could have demanded a ransom and accomplished their goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.24,0:10:39.53,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Is there any reason for them to keep it a secret and sell him off?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.53,0:10:42.07,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know why they'd keep it a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.07,0:10:45.45,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But selling him off has a simple and clear reasoning.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.45,0:10:48.04,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,They were pissed off.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.79,0:10:56.67,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Mafias and cartels can't stand having shit rubbed in their faces.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.67,0:10:57.47,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.73,0:11:17.53,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Revy, if their face is what's at stake, then this is going to be a hassle.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.40,0:11:23.41,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to put a little insurance on our package before we deliver it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.87,0:11:27.62,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'll ask Balalaika to see what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.45,0:11:29.41,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.41,0:11:33.29,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's rare to have Dutch asking a favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.29,0:11:37.05,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Details about the Manisarera cartel and the Loveless family.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.05,0:11:39.09,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Can you prepare that for us?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.09,0:11:40.80,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Ohh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.80,0:11:45.30,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We've actually just got a job in, concerning Manisarera.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.30,0:11:47.60,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You have good timing, Dutch.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.60,0:11:49.68,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, I owe you one.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.68,0:11:55.48,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But since we're still just setting up the insurance, can I ask that you don't stir things up?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.48,0:11:57.61,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well that's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.61,0:11:58.19,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.44,0:12:05.50,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,In our business, when things get stirred up, they get stirred up like a typhoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.78,0:12:09.29,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Just do your best, do it cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.29,0:12:10.54,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,OK, OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.54,0:12:11.96,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Do I respond to your office?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.96,0:12:16.25,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No. We'll be having a drink at the Yellow Flag.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.30,0:12:20.76,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,All right then, Rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.76,0:12:24.43,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There's one more thing we need to check out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.43,0:12:31.89,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Is Daddy Loveless the type to spend personal resources to deal with a hostage situation, like the kid says?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.39,0:12:34.06,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.06,0:12:39.02,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, they only have enough resources to keep one servant.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.02,0:12:41.03,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,A servant? What kind?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.49,0:12:43.83,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Just a house maid.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.36,0:12:48.33,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Think the maid's gonna rush in to save the little prince?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.33,0:12:49.41,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That'd be fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.57,0:14:05.28,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What did you just say?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.28,0:14:10.87,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I am just a lonely soul who has come all the way from South America.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.87,0:14:16.37,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I am in search of a place where I can find my countryman.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.25,0:14:20.00,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,From your country?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.00,0:14:21.76,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.09,0:14:29.85,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This little lady's countryman?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.59,0:14:32.76,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Could she mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.76,0:14:35.86,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There are no other South Americans in this area.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.27,0:14:39.81,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We can't really say...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.81,0:14:42.94,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Then, who might I ask that could tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.94,0:14:47.03,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Miss, there is a place where you might be able to find out, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.65,0:14:51.49,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...that place is like a den of gangsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.49,0:14:52.66,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I do not mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.66,0:14:56.29,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So long as I can find out about my countryman there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.29,0:14:59.62,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Miss, I really wouldn't recommend the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.62,0:15:01.58,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Please do not worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.26,0:15:11.18,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We're here. It's land.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.01,0:15:14.18,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.77,0:15:20.98,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's not the disposition of an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.98,0:15:23.02,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You were a brat once too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.65,0:15:26.32,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Then pay me as a baby-sitter.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.32,0:15:27.53,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.53,0:15:28.36,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Revy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.36,0:15:29.62,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Get in!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.07,0:15:33.03,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, isn't that enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.03,0:15:34.75,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What? You too?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.62,0:15:41.00,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You gonna treat him nice and get a job at his house?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.00,0:15:48.21,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You'd be better off as a white-faced butler than as a sailor.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.21,0:15:50.88,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I see. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.88,0:15:56.35,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Asking, "Master, how would you like your Mint Julep?"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.35,0:15:58.31,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Just like Old Black Joe,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.31,0:16:02.19,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,surrounded by a dozen other servants and having a dandy ol' time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.19,0:16:06.65,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I told you before, we only have one servant.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.65,0:16:08.95,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,A maid named Roberta.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.36,0:16:12.22,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And even though she's a maid, she's no good at cleaning or chores.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.00,0:16:23.79,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have milk here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.79,0:16:26.05,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Then may I have a water?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.75,0:16:31.88,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I only arrived here today, and I do not know my way around.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.88,0:16:33.64,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I am in search of a Colombian friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.73,0:16:46.66,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This is a bar. Order a real drink, idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.44,0:16:54.11,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I've only arrived here today, and I do not know my way around.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.11,0:16:56.83,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I am in search of a Colombian friend of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.37,0:17:00.74,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Might you know where the proper authorities are?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.74,0:17:05.46,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Lady, does this look like the tourist department or an employment bureau?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.46,0:17:06.38,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.34,0:17:10.75,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,She's a klutz.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.75,0:17:13.09,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,She can't clean or do chores but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.09,0:17:13.80,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,but,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.63,0:17:16.93,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Roberta is a lot stronger than you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.43,0:17:26.15,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Of all the god-damned things to say!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.15,0:17:30.36,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,She's not going to throw a teapot at me, is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.32,0:17:42.54,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If that's true, I'll believe that Jesus blazed across Route 66 in a chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.16,0:17:46.67,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Have you seen her strength?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.67,0:17:50.26,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't, but I remember one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.67,0:17:57.84,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We lived at my father's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.84,0:18:02.90,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We lived peacefully, Roberta, my father and I.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.11,0:18:17.62,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't have many friends to play with, so she played with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.53,0:18:22.08,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I loved to arm wrestle.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.53,0:18:26.00,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Because I could beat Roberta every time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.00,0:18:29.30,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Roberta lost every single time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.88,0:18:33.42,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,She was arm wrestling me on that day, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.42,0:18:34.76,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,when...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.88,0:18:36.80,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...they came.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.97,0:18:39.80,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,To threaten my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.72,0:18:48.85,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,She knew what was going on, long before I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.85,0:18:52.68,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,She hardened up as soon as she realized they were coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.23,0:18:58.16,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I tried to beat her with my usual amount of strength, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.03,0:19:04.84,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,her arm was like steel.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.41,0:19:10.37,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Roberta always lost to me on purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.37,0:19:15.59,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,She had a reason to always act like a weak maid.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.59,0:19:17.17,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I found out then.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.13,0:19:56.00,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Fallen nobility.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.00,0:19:58.51,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The wife died four years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.96,0:20:06.35,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The ones pictured are, the head, Diego; his only son, Garcia; and their only servant, the house maid.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.35,0:20:08.06,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.06,0:20:09.54,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't good.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.23,0:20:14.44,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Comrade Sergeant. Take a look at her eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.44,0:20:15.36,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you notice anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.86,0:20:18.48,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The eyes of a soldier.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.48,0:20:20.36,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That is correct, Sergeant.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.82,0:20:22.86,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And that's not all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.86,0:20:24.87,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,She's one hell of a wild dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.12,0:20:29.88,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Woman, I've got business with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.29,0:20:36.38,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I heard a woman in a strange maid's outfit is looking for the Colombian mafia.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.22,0:20:41.55,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,In a crazy outfit that you'd only see in Hollywood movies...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.55,0:20:45.39,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,any idiot would remember someone in clothes like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.05,0:20:49.81,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You called us here, what are you after?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.81,0:20:50.89,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.36,0:20:59.86,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted you to find me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.86,0:21:03.36,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You are from the Manisarera cartel, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.36,0:21:06.66,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I am a servant of the Loveless family.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.66,0:21:08.92,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I have a few things I would like to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.62,0:21:14.00,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you'll excuse me, but I am afraid I may have to be rude.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.71,0:21:16.33,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Did you hear that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.33,0:21:18.63,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Be rude? This bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.63,0:21:20.42,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,She's making me laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.42,0:21:22.38,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What are you gonna do, miss?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.38,0:21:24.88,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm afraid I will not be able to hold back.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.88,0:21:26.89,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Please pardon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.55,0:21:30.40,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Please enjoy yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.27,0:21:33.18,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Roberta!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.95,0:23:17.83,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.04,0:23:19.50,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.50,0:23:21.92,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's a killer robot from the future!
